headline: Has TJX Stock’s Strong Multi Year Run Left Limited Upside For 2025?
summary: If you are wondering whether TJX Companies is still a bargain after such a strong run, or if the easy money has already been made, this article walks through what the numbers say about its value. The stock has climbed 0.9% over the last week and 6.7% over the last month, and is up 26.5% year to date, building on gains of 23.1% over 1 year, 104.7% over 3 years, and 149.9% over 5 years. Those moves have come as investors continue to lean into off-price retail as a defensive way to navigate...
